XML:
layouts:
main layouts are linear layout and Relative layout.
----------------------------1.LINEAR LAYOUT:-----------------------


linear layout have two different properties.
1.horiozontal and 2.vertical. --> also called orientation of linear layouts.
gravity is a attribute of this layout..

--------------------2.Relative layout---------------------
relative layout is good for everything. 
there have relations in between root layout and child views.
and also have relations between child views together.
some relations:
1.alignParentBottom, alignParentRight, alignParentLeft,layoutAbove,layoutbelow;
2.centerInParent.
